.custom-after-search {

  .custom-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    width: calc(100% - 0.4rem);
    margin: 0.3rem auto 0;

    .left-nav,
    .right-tips {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .left-nav {
      border-radius: 6px;
      overflow: hidden;

      p {
        width: 1.6rem;
        height: 0.56rem;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 0.56rem;
        background-color: #ECEDEE;
        font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;
        font-size: 0.24rem;
        color: #333333;

        &.active {
          color: white;
          @include background-theme("main");
        }
      }
    }

    .right-tips {
      .circle {
        width: 0.18rem;
        height: 0.18rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #E02020;
        margin-right: 0.08rem;
      }

      p {
        font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;
        font-size: 0.24rem;
        color: #333333;
      }
    }
  }

  .van-swipe-cell {
    // @include background-theme-opacity("normal", 0.8);
    // @include background-theme("normal");
    @include background-theme-lighten("main", 30%);
    border-radius: 0.06rem;
    width: calc(100% - 0.4rem);
    margin: 0.3rem auto 0;

    .custom-content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      justify-content: space-between;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0.2rem;

      .left-content {
        flex: 1 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;

        .neighborhood-committee-name {
          font-family: PingFangSC-Medium;
          color: #ffffff;
          line-height: 32px;
          font-size: 0.32rem;
        }

        .number-wrap {
          width: 100%;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          margin-top: 0.1rem;

          .number-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;

            p {
              font-family: PingFangSC-Medium;
              color: #ffffff;
              letter-spacing: 0;
              line-height: 1 !important;
              font-size: 0.32rem !important;
              margin-right: 0.04rem;

              &.small-font {
                font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;
                color: #FFFFFF;
                letter-spacing: 0;
                font-size: 0.24rem !important;
                margin: 0 0 0.02rem 0;
                opacity: 0.5;
              }

              &.margin-font {
                margin: 0 0.07rem;
              }
            }

            &:nth-child(1),
            &:nth-child(2) {
              width: 1.6rem;
            }

            &:nth-child(3) {
              width: auto;
            }
          }
        }
      }

      .right-icon {
        width: 0.6rem;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      &.active {
        // @include background-theme-opacity("normal", 0.6);

        p {
          color: white !important;
        }
      }
    }

    .change-record {
      height: 100%;
      width: 1.3rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      @include background-theme("main");

      p {
        font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;
        color: #FFFFFF;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 0.32rem;
        font-size: 0.24rem;
      }

      .iconfont {
        font-size: 0.42rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.13rem;
        color: white;
      }
    }

  }

}

          color: #999999 !important;
          font-size: 0.4rem !important;
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
